  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0dca\u0d85\u0dbd\u0dd2 \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9c\u0ddc\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dba\u0ddd \u0dad\u0dd4\u0db1\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Three farmers were killed by wild elephant attacks",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police say that three farmers have been killed in three wild elephant attacks in Polonnaruwa, Dimbulagala, Medirigiriya Navanagara and Saliyawewa Nilabamma Fort area.",
        "D.B.T.G., a resident of Madirigiriya Navanagara. Sarathchandra, a 65-year-old father of three, also 47-year-old D.M., a resident of Dimbulagala Palatia. Seneviratne Banda, a 47-year-old father of three, also a resident of Saliyawewa Neelabamma area, R.P.D. A 76-year-old farmer named Pemadasa has also died.",
        "DM The police also mention that Seneviratne Banda is the husband of a member of the Dimbulagala local council. He also works as an Institutional Development Officer at Weheragala Divisional Office in Mahaweli C Region. Yesterday at 2.30 this wild elephant was attacked while guarding the paddy fields to protect the paddy from the wild elephants coming to the field. He was attacked by elephants and was taken to Manampitiya Hospital by his neighbors and later transferred to Polonnaruwa Hospital for further treatment. The police say that he was dead when he was taken to the Polonnaruwa hospital.",
        "Sarathchandra, a father of three, who was attacked by wild elephants in Medirigiri Navanagara, went with a friend to Darshanapura to protect his farmland from wild elephants, when a wild elephant chased them.",
        "Later, they ran to a nearby house, but the police said that the elephant killed them when they fell while running.",
        "A farmer named Saliyawewa Pemadasa was attacked by wild elephants when he came out of his house for some need."
      ],
